      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know you mean well but it doesn't feel like that. it feels like i'm just taking up space and energy that they could be using for their own families. sometimes i think it would be more peaceful for everyone if i just wasn't around to cause all this trouble. like, wouldn't they be better off if i just stopped fighting it?",
